entries.femaleVariant: Never thought about giving it all up?
Be better off asking my boss if he ever thought about becoming a pacifist.
It's just... you hear about all those accidents in cyberspace... You're not scared your brain'll get barbecued one day?
Sure, if I was freelancing from home. But when you're with Militech, you plow through the net like a Basilisk.
The net's just one side of the coin though.
I heard if someone's jacked in and dies in real life... they're trapped in there forever.
Mhm. You're right. And then they grow tentacles and turn into demons.
C'mon, you're too old to believe in scary stories.
